# XV6 OS Project - Custom Features

## 📌 Project Description
This project modifies the XV6 operating system by adding new features:
- sysinfo system call
- mytop command (process viewer)
- setpriority system call
- Priority-based scheduler

## ⚙️ How to Run
1. Clone the repository:
   git clone https://github.com/pankajsharma0001/xv6-os-project.git

2. Go to folder:
   cd xv6-os-project

3. Build and run:
   make clean
   make qemu

## 🧪 Features and Testing

### sysinfo
$ sysinfo

### mytop
$ mytop

### setpriority
$ setpriority <pid> <priority>
